00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:24.190
And he was gathering not
only accounts of this voyage

00:22:24.190 --> 00:22:25.490
but of several other voyages

00:22:25.490 --> 00:22:29.100
and he was writing a history
of the kingdom of Peru.

00:22:29.100 --> 00:22:32.720
And his work comes up later
because he was paying attention

00:22:32.720 --> 00:22:34.430
to other things that
were being reported

00:22:34.430 --> 00:22:36.450
and then he gets cited as well.

00:22:36.450 --> 00:22:38.840
So part of what I'm doing, even
