00:25:23.330 --> 00:25:27.040
where they are was
actually quite prevalent.

00:25:27.040 --> 00:25:29.650
Which I suppose I should
have expected.

00:25:29.650 --> 00:25:35.230
And then as a sort of
middle of the road map,

00:25:35.230 --> 00:25:39.220 position:56%
