00:26:52.260 --> 00:26:57.080
I hate to mysterious
but no I love it.

00:26:57.080 --> 00:27:01.540
Is that we get the, the Parime lake
which I've tried to highlight here

00:27:01.540 --> 00:27:04.960
and again a slightly
closer view of it.

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:06.890
Which is the lake of gold.

00:27:06.890 --> 00:27:15.150
And it's in the Guianas, it
might also be referenced as Manao

00:27:15.150 --> 00:27:18.550
but it's the first time that
